{"tid":613240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警搗「Part time情人」檢鹹濕骰仔 印有 「舔」、「吻」等字","createTime":"2018-04-01T13:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T15:09:47.000Z","uid":5195,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ccddfc655e699aff546a7438b7b31c50777745","tid":613240,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:39:21.000Z","msg":"警方打擊青少年援交拘捕19人。旺角警區特別職務隊根據線報及經深入調查後，採取「山河」行動，於3月30及31日，派出多名探員「放蛇」喬裝顧客，共拘捕13男6女（16至40歲），當中1男為中介人，6男為顧客，另有6男6女分別為「Part time boyfriend (兼職男友)」及「Part time girlfriend(兼職女友) 」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，被捕的兼職情人中，有2名印尼女子，包括一名30歲家傭，另一名40歲的則曾為家傭，現被揭逾期居留。另3男報稱為學生，分別為大專生、九龍區的中學生及就讀職訓局。另有7人報稱無業及從事售貨員，包括年齡最細的16歲少女。<br />\n<br />\n行動中檢獲一批護士服、水手裝等情趣衣物，以及一批潤滑劑、避孕套等證物，另亦有「鹹濕骰仔」，上面印有 「舔」、「吻」等字，懷疑是援交時作遊戲之用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180401/photo/bkn-20180401144554343-0401_00822_001_08b.jpg?20180401190637\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180401%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180401144554343-0401_00822_001_08b.jpg%3F20180401190637&h=4d5d0697&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b06bfd555e0dfd3c8ce803db6dd9ad524799bfba","tid":613240,"uid":101110,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:42:24.000Z","msg":"擺嗰個都幾有心機<br />\n特登放到幾隻字都睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2e29b5a0e61d92115463aaa005329e5a88aaba","tid":613240,"uid":24160,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/c7MXW9r.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fc7MXW9r.gif&h=22fdd86f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b912f839b33d490edfcf2e6681e620d48af5d3df","tid":613240,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e2e29b5a0e61d92115463aaa005329e5a88aaba","tid":613240,"uid":24160,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.co